Topic.Title: Summary of Weekly Petroleum Data for the Week Ending June 28, 2013

Message.Msg: Weekly Natural Gas Storage Report for week ending June 28, 2013 Released: July 3, 2013 at 12:00 p.m. Summary Working gas in storage was 2,605 Bcf as of Friday, June 28, 2013, according to EIA estimates. This represents a net increase of 72 Bcf from the previous week. Stocks were 491 Bcf less than last year at this time and 30 Bcf below the 5-year average of 2,635 Bcf. In the East Region, stocks were 92 Bcf below the 5-year average following net injections of 48 Bcf. Stocks in the Producing Region were 19 Bcf above the 5-year average of 952 Bcf after a net injection of 14 Bcf. Stocks in the West Region were 43 Bcf above the 5-year average after a net addition of 10 Bcf. At 2,605 Bcf, total working gas is within the 5-year historical range. eia

Obama is the gift that keeps on giving. I do believe there will be an independence day celebration for one tormented soul after all now... The dear sweet American Fräulein who is staying with us broken down emotionally yesterday evening – 4 July – and expressed herself in the most revealing of ways for a woman. She cried over her terrible prospects in the USA. She blames the people, that is the races other than her own, who put Obama in and maintain control of the US today. Out of the sweet lips of a damsel came things I could not write on this board or they would surely be censored. Her platinum blonde hair contrasted with her flushed face and shined magically. Her blue eyes overflowed with tears. She was very vulnerable and sexy. But I’m impervious to attraction to a female when I have my luscious Freyja right near by. So I phoned a friend of mine from my gymnasium days, in Düsseldorf, who I know shares sentiments exactly like she does. Although he does not have to put up with people like Obama. His father worked in the defence industry and he does too. He is single. Once she cleared up some I placed her on the video phone. The two of them spent several hours talking together. He’s coming to visit today for the weekend to meet her in the flesh. He surely knows how to unlock the door to her secrets now. I think she will be on her way to Düsseldorf by Monday. He’s a gentleman and can take care of her problems easily. Obama should apply for a role as Cupid. He’s missed his calling.
